---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Playwright Testing for React Applications | E2E Testing Guide 2025"
  description="Playwright end-to-end testing for React enterprise applications with quality gates and CI/CD integration from O2 implementation."
>
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col gap-12">
    <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="text-sm text-slate-400">
      <a href="/" class="transition hover:text-accent">Home</a>
      <span class="mx-2">→</span>
      <a href="/vocabulary" class="transition hover:text-accent">Vocabulary</a>
      <span class="mx-2">→</span>
      <span class="text-slate-200">Playwright Testing</span>
    </nav>

    <section class="space-y-4">
      <p class="eyebrow">Testing & Quality</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white sm:text-5xl">Playwright Testing</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">Reliable end-to-end testing for React applications</p>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-[32px] border border-accent/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-transparent p-8 shadow-card">
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-100">
        <strong class="text-white">Definition:</strong> Playwright is an end-to-end testing framework for React applications with multi-browser support, auto-wait, video recording, and trace viewer for reliable automated testing.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="surface-card space-y-6">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Playwright Advantages</h2>
      </div>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-200">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Multi-browser testing:</strong> Chromium, Firefox, WebKit support</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Auto-wait:</strong> Eliminates flaky tests with smart waiting</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Trace viewer:</strong> Debug test failures with timeline and screenshots</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent"></span>
          <span><strong class="text-white">Parallel execution:</strong> Fast CI/CD pipelines</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="surface-card space-y-6">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow text-accent">Case Study</p>
        <h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Real Implementation: O2 Czech Republic</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-200">
        The <strong class="text-white">O2 Service Workbench</strong> uses Playwright quality gates in CI/CD, running 40+ E2E scenarios covering ticket workflows, authentication, and real-time updates—catching 15+ regression bugs before production.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Related Vocabulary</h3>
      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <a href="/vocabulary/docker-github-actions-cicd" class="grid-panel">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-accent">Docker GitHub Actions CI/CD</h4>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Automated testing in deployment pipeline</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/vocabulary/react-typescript" class="grid-panel">
          <h4 class="font-semibold text-accent">React TypeScript</h4>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-300">Type-safe component testing</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="rounded-[32px] border border-accent/30 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-transparent p-8 text-center shadow-card">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Need E2E Testing Setup?</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-lg text-slate-200">I implement Playwright testing strategies for enterprise React applications.</p>
      <a href="mailto:marekdolnicek@gmail.com" class="mt-6 inline-block rounded-full bg-accent px-8 py-3 font-semibold text-ink shadow-card transition hover:bg-accentMuted">Get in touch</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
